### ============================================
### COURSE VALIDATION TESTING
### ============================================
### Test the real-time course validation endpoint
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminEmail = sharma@amu.ac.in
@adminPassword = Teacher@123
@token = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### 1. LOGIN AS ADMIN (Get Token First)
### ============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

### Copy the token from response and replace @token above

### ============================================
### 2. CHECK EXISTING COURSE CODE (Should Return True)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses/check?courseCode=COA2131
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response:
### {
###   "courseCodeExists": true,
###   "existingCourseCode": {
###     "course_code": "COA2131",
###     "course_name": "Data Structures"
###   }
### }

### ============================================
### 3. CHECK EXISTING COURSE CODE (Case Insensitive)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses/check?courseCode=coa2131
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: Should still find the course (case-insensitive)

### ============================================
### 4. CHECK NON-EXISTING COURSE CODE (Should Return False)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses/check?courseCode=COA9999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response:
### {
###   "courseCodeExists": false
### }

### ============================================
### 5. CHECK EXISTING COURSE NAME (Should Return True)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses/check?courseName=Data%20Structures
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response:
### {
###   "courseNameExists": true,
###   "existingCourseName": {
###     "course_code": "COA2131",
###     "course_name": "Data Structures"
###   }
### }

### ============================================
### 6. CHECK EXISTING COURSE NAME (Case Insensitive)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses/check?courseName=data%20structures
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: Should still find the course (case-insensitive)

### ============================================
### 7. CHECK NON-EXISTING COURSE NAME (Should Return False)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses/check?courseName=Advanced%20Quantum%20Computing
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response:
### {
###   "courseNameExists": false
### }

### ============================================
### 8. CHECK BOTH CODE AND NAME (Existing)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses/check?courseCode=COA2131&courseName=Data%20Structures
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response:
### {
###   "courseCodeExists": true,
###   "courseNameExists": true,
###   "existingCourseCode": {...},
###   "existingCourseName": {...}
### }

### ============================================
### 9. CHECK BOTH CODE AND NAME (Mixed)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses/check?courseCode=COA9999&courseName=Data%20Structures
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response:
### {
###   "courseCodeExists": false,
###   "courseNameExists": true,
###   "existingCourseName": {...}
### }

### ============================================
### 10. CHECK WITHOUT PARAMETERS (Should Fail)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses/check
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response: 400 Bad Request
### {
###   "error": "Provide courseCode or courseName"
### }

### ============================================
### 11. CHECK WITHOUT TOKEN (Should Fail)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses/check?courseCode=COA2131

### Expected Response: 401 Unauthorized
### {
###   "error": "No token provided"
### }

### ============================================
### 12. CHECK AS NON-ADMIN (Should Fail)
### ============================================
### First login as student
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "gm7605@myamu.ac.in",
  "password": "azx"
}

### Then try to check (use student token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses/check?courseCode=COA2131
Authorization: Bearer STUDENT_TOKEN_HERE

### Expected Response: 403 Forbidden
### {
###   "error": "Admin access required"
### }

