### TESTING CHECKLIST
### ============================================
### ✅ Test 1: Admin login successful
### ✅ Test 2: Existing course code detected
### ✅ Test 3: Case-insensitive code matching works
### ✅ Test 4: Non-existing course code returns false
### ✅ Test 5: Existing course name detected
### ✅ Test 6: Case-insensitive name matching works
### ✅ Test 7: Non-existing course name returns false
### ✅ Test 8: Both parameters work together
### ✅ Test 9: Mixed results (one exists, one doesn't)
### ✅ Test 10: Missing parameters rejected
### ✅ Test 11: No token rejected
### ✅ Test 12: Non-admin access rejected

